iwells2.bio: I have been keenly interested in computer science since I was a freshman in high school and I took a computer programming course using ancient Microsoft QuickBasic. I was hooked when I saw my first "Hello World" flickering in a terminal; I felt like the machine was dancing at my fingertips. I am most interested in artificial intelligence and would like to see my name on a patent for the first thinking, feeling man-made system. That, and I want to live comfortably on top of a fat paycheck.
iwells2.name: Ian Wells
